casebody.data:
SOLIDFX, LLC, petitioner,
v.
JEPPESEN SANDERSON, INC. No. 16-1303. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 2, 2017. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Tenth Circuit denied. Justice ALITO and Justice GORSUCH took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
